videos.headline: Fresno State's McMaryion throws 38-yard deep ball to Johnson
videos.description: Marcus McMaryion connects with KeeSean Johnson on a 38-yard strike downfield to put the Bulldogs in scoring position.

videos.headline: McMaryion finds Johnson in back of end zone for TD
videos.description: Marcus McMaryion finds KeeSean Johnson in the back of the end zone for a touchdown putting Fresno State on top of Boise State 7-3.

videos.headline: Rypien picked off in the end zone
videos.description: Boise State's Brett Rypien is picked off by Fresno State's Juju Hughes on a deep pass to the end zone.

videos.headline: Rivers dives in for Fresno State TD
videos.description: Ronnie Rivers dives in from the 1 yard line for the Fresno State touchdown to push their lead over Boise State to 17-3.

videos.headline: Mattison scores second TD to tie game at 17-17
videos.description: Alexander Mattison scores his second touchdown of the night for Boise State and ties the game at 17-17.

videos.headline: Rypien connects with Shakir for 49-yard TD
videos.description: Brett Rypien finds Khalil Shakir deep downfield to score a 49-yard touchdown putting Boise State on top of Fresno State 24-17.

videos.headline: Boise State fan goes crazy after fourth-down stand
videos.description: Marcus McMaryion pass to KeeSean Johnson as it's broken up by Boise State's Avery Williams to seal the win.
